Both the follower and the leader algorithm consist of three main
parts. The b-interval wise update (Lines 2 âˆ’ 4) makes sure that ls
values are refreshed frequently. Lines 6 âˆ’ 33 (in case of a follower)
and Lines 5âˆ’24 (in case of a leader) are used for medium access in
