1.1. Our results
In this paper, we show how to produce schedules of length O(c + d) in O(m(c +
d)(log P)4 (log log P)) time steps, with probability at least 1âˆ’1/P Î´ , for any constant
Î´ > 0, where m is the number of distinct edges traversed by some packet in the
